## 3. Docker Fundamentals

Concepts Learned:

### Image

Blueprint/template.

Example:

```text
postgres:17
```

---

### Container

Running instance of an image.

Example:

```text
wealth_postgres
```

---

### Volume

Persistent storage.

Without volume:

```text
Container Deleted
    ↓
Data Lost
```

With volume:

```text
Container Deleted
    ↓
Data Preserved
```

---

### Port Mapping

```yaml
5432:5432
```

Meaning:

```text
Host Port      Container Port
5432     ->    5432
```

